HTML: Structure content and layout (header, hero section, features, testimonials, contact, etc.).

CSS: Style the page with elegant colors, fonts, and responsive layouts for various devices.

JavaScript: Add dynamic features such as animations, sliders, and interactive elements for engagement.

Navigation: Create a user-friendly, intuitive navigation bar for seamless browsing.

Responsiveness: Ensure the page looks great on desktops, tablets, and mobiles.

Creativity: Showcase your skills by blending design and functionality to make a memorable first impression.
